      "id": "5315919905"
    },
    {
      "id": "17137567105"
    }
  ]
}
```

For each deal, the response will include the date and time the splits were created or updated, the IDs of users splitting the deal, and the percentage of the deal amount assigned to each user.For two deals, the response would look similar to:
