```
{
  "inputs": [
    {
      "id": "123456"
    },
    {
      "id": "7891011"
    },
    {
      "id": "12123434"
    }
  ]
}
```

​

## Limits

Object API batch endpoints are limited to 100 inputs per request. For example, create or retrieve up to 100 contacts per request.
